    "cough_care_5_10": {
      "message": "👉 Alerid syrup 7.5 ml at night × 3 days\n👉 Benadryl Cough Formula 5 ml thrice daily × 3 days\n⏱️ If cough > 3 days or child weak → consult doctor.\n💨 Steam inhalation × 3/day. Encourage fluids."
    },
    "cough_care_10plus": {
